  h1 As a Man Thinketh
  p This book will help you understand how your thoughts shape your character, circumstances, and, ultimately, your destiny.
  
  h2 Effect of Thought on Circumstances
  p Just as a gardener cultivates his plot, keeping it free from weeds, and growing the flowers and fruits which he requires, so may a man tend the garden of his mind, weeding out all the wrong, useless, and impure thoughts, and cultivating toward perfection the flowers and fruits of right, useful, and pure thoughts.
